data.description: Rare find mid-century expanded colonial overlooking beautiful Central Park! The layout and design is unmatched, featuring a 1st floor bedroom & full bath + 3 large bedrooms on 2nd w/ master bath shared w/ hallway! Nice kitchen w/ wrap around laminate counters, range and ss fridge stays. Brand new carpeting to very spacious 2nd floor complimented w/ large closets in all rooms. 1st and 2nd floor decks overlook the rear yard. Roomy and clean full basement freshly painted. Large brick and block garage for easy conversion to 2-car. Seller is providing a 1 year home warranty! Ready to occupy, check out the pics!
